{"word":"παραγίνομαι","slug":"παραγίνομαι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>παραγίνομαι</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:παρά\">παρά</a>, <a class=\"S\" href=\"S:γίνομαι\">γίνομαι</a></el>] ‘make one’s way so as to be present’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> of reaching a position <b>come, arrive, be present <a href='B:470 2:1'>Mt 2:1</a>; <a href='B:480 14:43'>Mk 14:43</a>; <a href='B:490 7:4'>Lk 7:4</a>; <a href='B:490 11:6'>11:6</a>; <a href='B:490 14:21'>14:21</a>; <a href='B:500 3:23'>J 3:23</a>; <a href='B:510 5:21'>Ac 5:21</a></b> and <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ oft.\">oft.</a> in Ac; <b><a href='B:530 16:3'>1 Cor 16:3</a>.</b> In a supportive role <b><a href='B:620 4:16'>2 Ti 4:16</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of being at a position in public <b>be on the scene, appear in public <a href='B:470 3:1'>Mt 3:1</a>; <a href='B:490 12:51'>Lk 12:51</a>; <a href='B:650 9:11'>Hb 9:11</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:παραγένωμαι\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:παράγω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}